name: stock_buffer_on_hand_list
query:
select item_code as "Material::120",
       actual_qty as "On Hand::100",
       incoming_dlt_qty as "On Supply::100",
       qualified_demand as "Demand::100",
	   net_flow_position as "Available::100",
	   procure_recommended_qty as "Recommended Qty::100",
	   planning_priority_level as "Plan Level::90",
	   execution_priority_level as "Execution Level::90",
	   net_flow_position_percent as "Available Percent ::90",
	   on_hand_percent as "On Hand Percent::90"
from `tabStock Buffer`
